data.description: Welcome to this timeless farmhouse that seamlessly blends historic charm with modern comforts. Step into the heart of the home – a farmhouse kitchen that whispers tales of days gone by, complete with rustic details and a warm, inviting atmosphere. The clawfoot tub is an unexpected luxury. The original wood floors in the living room exude character, while a wood-burning stove adds both warmth and nostalgia to the space. Upstairs, discover a master bedroom with a mezzanine, offering a unique and cozy retreat. The clawfoot tub in the bathroom beckons relaxation. Whether you work from home or simply need a tranquil space for creativity, the dedicated office provides the perfect setting. A modern addition to this historic gem is the spacious garage, offering ample storage for all your modern needs. This 1899 farmhouse is not just a house; it's a story waiting to be continued. Come experience the charm, history, and warmth that define this unique property.
